metadata.name: Meta COSer Club #1
metadata.description: A commemorative NFT collection for COS.TV and COS.SPACE with a collection size of 101 featuring art by Vietnamese 3D graphics studio, 3DVIETPRO. Meta COSer Club represents the belief that anyone can be a creator. Owners will receive special benefits in the Contentos ecosystem on COS.TV and COS.SPACE.
